      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ").",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Elkanah, as \"second to the king,\" was probably the chief of the royal counselors. ",
        "children": [
